                        li API key authentication
                        li Minor UI changes and fixes

        h4 01-10-2020
            h5
                ul(style="font-family: monospace, Consolas")
                    i
                        li Error messages correctly displayed on index page in info/alert/succes box
                        li /userInfo API returns whole user object

        h4 06-10-2020
            h5
                ul(style="font-family: monospace, Consolas")
                    i
                        li Error messages correctly displayed on every page now
                        li User profile system introduced
                        li Edit user settings (email, password, username, etc)
                        li Profile picture (with ability to change it)
