                        li Map is now more responsive and faster (moved most of CPU intensive tasks to server)
                        li Map is now A LOT MORE FASTER, changed default bitmap renderer to Canvas and png markers to dynamically rendered
                        li Map now group markers in 80px radius into groups, which can be interacted with (zoom at group, expand group)
                        li Removed unused packages
                        li General codebase cleanup
                        li User page buttons replaced with better looking cards
                        li Load leaflet from CDN only at /map, not on every page (lol)
